abstract: College Basketball Roundup; University of South Carolina women's basketball team beats Mississippi State University, 69-50; other women's and men's college basketball scores noted.
lead_paragraph: Tiffany Mitchell scored 16 points, and No. 2 South Carolina defeated No. 11 Mississippi State to clinch a share of its second straight Southeastern Conference regular-season title.
